criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion criteria:

          -  adult patient ;

          -  first CT-PET 18 FDG realized for the inital staging ;

          -  absence of previous treatment for a thoracic neoplasm ;

          -  biopsy realized on the primitive site or local drainage lymphadenopathy ;

          -  primitive site viewable with morphological imagery ;

          -  availability of evaluation of PDL1's overexpression ;

        Exclusion criteria

        - Refusal to participate in this research
